Age Calculator
📌 Project Overview
The Age Calculator is a simple web application that calculates a user's exact age based on their date of birth. It displays the age in years, months, and days using JavaScript date functions.
🚀 Features
Calculate age instantly from date of birth
Displays age in years, months, and days
User-friendly interface
Responsive design for mobile and desktop
Input validation for accurate results
🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript (ES6)
📂 How to Use
Enter your date of birth.
Click the Calculate Age button.
View your age displayed in years, months, and days.
🎯 Learning Outcomes
Working with JavaScript Date objects
DOM manipulation
Form validation
Responsive web design
